ing: 1 (12 ounce) package crabmeat, flaked and cartilage removed
n: Crab Rangoon Dip for the Slow Cooker
des: "A delicious, creamy dip similar to the filling in crab rangoons. Serve with crackers."
ins:
Mix cream cheese, crabmeat, sour cream, green onions, confectioners' sugar, Worcestershire sauce, and garlic powder in the crock of a slow cooker.
Cook on Low for 2 hours, stirring at least once.
